Section: kde
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Replaces: kdebase-workspace-bin (<< 3.95.0)
Provides: x-window-manager
Description: the KDE window manager
 This package contains the KDE window manager, featuring hardware-accelerated
 compositing effects.
 .
 This package is part of the KDE 4 base workspace module.

Package: systemsettings
Section: kde
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: KDE System Settings Center
 KDE System Settings is an improved user interface for configuring the desktop
 and other aspects of the system.
 .
 This package is part of the KDE 4 base workspace module.

Package: kdebase-workspace-dbg
Section: devel
Architecture: any
Priority: extra
Depends: kdebase-workspace (= ${source:Version}), kdepimlibs-dbg
Description: debugging symbols for kdebase-workspace
 This package contains the debugging symbols associated with kdebase-workspace.
 They will automatically be used by gdb for debugging kdebase-workspace-related
 issues.

